author: Patricia Garcia
title: 20 Secret Celebrity Weddings We Still Know Little About
text: There are few things a celebrity couple loves more than getting married in a surprise secret wedding. Allison Williams and Ricky Van Veen have just joined the club of those who have pulled off the admirable feat of getting married out of the public eye. Here, we take a look back at twenty celebrity duos who surprised us all with their undercover weddings.
